## 5. Agentic Interaction Rules (Updated for MCP)

Add this to your AI Agent routing rules:

| Action | Required Architectural Step |
| --- | --- |
| **New Tool Added** | Define the schema in L1. Add the interface to `ToolRegistry` (L2). Implement the concrete HTTP/MCP logic in L3. |
| **Swapping Providers** | (e.g., Local Search -> Azure). Create a new adapter in L3 and update the Dependency Injection container/Composition Root in L4 to bind the new adapter to the L2 Port. Do not touch L1 or L2. |
